## 作业3：这两个query，用join能不能写？
#### 1.两个query

```SQL
select * from t_employee2 WHERE sal > (
select sal from t_employee2 WHERE ename='SMITH');

select * from t_employee2 WHERE (sal, job) = (
select sal,job from t_employee2 where ename = 'smith');
```
#### 2.用join的写法
**执行命令如下:**

```SQL
    SELECT * FROM t_employee2;
    DELIMITER $$
    CREATE PROCEDURE proce_employee_sal1 ()    # proce_employee_sal1表示所要创建的存储过程名字
    BEGIN
        SELECT sal
	      FROM t_employee2;
    END$$
    DELIMITER ;

    CALL proce_employee_sal1();                # 查询所有雇员的工资
```
